1939;;Three Smart Girls Grow Up;;American;;Henry Koster;;Deanna Durbin, Nan Grey, Helen Parrish;;musical comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three_Smart_Girls_Grow_Up;;Written by Felix Jackson and Bruce Manning, the film is about three sisters who believe life is going to be easy now that their parents are back together, until one sister falls in love with another's fiance, and the youngest sister plays matchmaker.[2]